C# Minebot, First Edition is brought to you thanks to the following people: umby24, SinZ.
C# Minebot is a rewrite of Visual Basic Minebot in the language C# (CSharp) The reasons I have for rewriting this program are 3 fold.
1. People always complain that it 'pains' them to look at VB Code 2. The last bot deperatly needed a rewrite due to my messiness of code 3. I wanted to learn C#.
So with that, I owe a few people credit for their code which I have used, or based my own code on in this project.
SinZ: The wrapped socket library I created for use is a rewrite of his "SinZationalSockets" library.
SirCmpwn: The vast majority of my code for protocol encryption belongs to this guy. The code was taken from his project 'SMProxy'.
and now, for links to the projects which I based / took code from.
